cff-version: 1.2.0
message: If you use this work, please cite it using the metadata below.
type: dataset
title: Experimental Results Dataset for Distributed Network Performance Measurement
abstract: This dataset contains results from experiments conducted across three nodes
  measuring performance under various network conditions configured via scripts like
  topology.file. Logs detailing system operations and energy usage were captured during
  each run iteration, providing insights into resource consumption and behavior. The
  measurements focus on data transfer efficiency and reliability metrics influenced
  by the specified Quality of Service parameters. Data artifacts are structured for
  analysis and visualization purposes related to these experimental findings.
